<paragraph blockId="1.[151,1437,968,1319]" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">
The 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Moore" authorityYear="1872" box="[201,424,968,995]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Agrisius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fuliginosus">
<emphasis box="[201,424,968,995]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">Agrisius fuliginosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
species-group is established by 
<bibRefCitation author="Dubatolov, V. V. &amp; Kishida, Y." box="[784,1105,968,995]" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" pagination="156 - 160" refId="ref5100" refString="Dubatolov, V. V. &amp; Kishida, Y. (2013) Remarks on the species composition of the genus Agrisius, with a description of a new species from Laos (Lepidoptera, Arctiidae: Lithosiinae). Tinea, 22 (3), 156 - 160." type="journal article" year="2013">Dubatolov &amp; Kishida (2013)</bibRefCitation>
for three species: 
<taxonomicName authority="Moore, 1872" authorityName="Moore" authorityYear="1872" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Agrisius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="fuliginosus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">A. fuliginosus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Moore, F." box="[193,337,1005,1031]" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" pagination="555 - 583" refId="ref5308" refString="Moore, F. (1872) Descriptions of new Indian Lepidoptera. Proceedings of the Zoological Society of London, 1872, 555 - 583, pls. XXXII-XXXIV." type="journal article" year="1872">Moore, 1872</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from N 
<collectingCountry box="[429,489,1004,1030]" name="India" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">India</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[500,570,1004,1030]" name="Nepal" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">Nepal</collectingCountry>
, 
<taxonomicName authority="Orhant, 1997" authorityName="Orhant" authorityYear="1997" box="[580,834,1004,1031]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Agrisius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="albula">
<emphasis box="[580,682,1004,1031]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">A. albula</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Orhant, G." box="[688,834,1004,1031]" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" pagination="33 - 35" refId="ref5339" refString="Orhant, G. (1997) Agrisius albula n. sp. (Arctiidae - Lithosiinae). Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de Mulhouse, 1997 (Juillet Septembre), 33 - 35. [in French]" type="journal article" year="1997">Orhant, 1997</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[901,1010,1005,1031]" name="Myanmar" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">Myanmar</collectingCountry>
(described for female), and 
<taxonomicName authority="Orhant, 2012" authorityName="Orhant" authorityYear="2012" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Agrisius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bolovena">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">A. bolovena</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Orhant, G." box="[185,333,1040,1067]" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" pagination="37 - 38" refId="ref5380" refString="Orhant, G. (2012) Deux nouveaux Agrisius orientaux (Lepidoptera, Arctiidae, Lithosiinae). Bulletin de la Societe entomologique de Mulhouse, 68 (3), 37 - 38. [in French]" type="journal article" year="2012">Orhant, 2012</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from S. 
<collectingCountry box="[428,482,1041,1067]" name="Laos" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">Laos</collectingCountry>
(with noted to possibly a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Orhant" authorityYear="1997" box="[981,1084,1040,1067]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Agrisius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="albula">
<emphasis box="[981,1084,1040,1067]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">A. albula</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
). Singh &amp; 
<bibRefCitation author="Kirti, J. S. &amp; Singh, N." box="[1206,1340,1040,1067]" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" refId="ref5275" refString="Kirti, J. S. &amp; Singh, N. (2016) Arctiid Moths of India. Vol. 2. Nature Books India, New Delhi, 214 pp." type="book" year="2016">Kirti (2016)</bibRefCitation>
(in 
<bibRefCitation author="Kirti, J. S. &amp; Singh, N." pageId="1" pageNumber="568" refId="ref5275" refString="Kirti, J. S. &amp; Singh, N. (2016) Arctiid Moths of India. Vol. 2. Nature Books India, New Delhi, 214 pp." type="book" year="2016">Kirti &amp; Singh 2016</bibRefCitation>
) later described two additional new species from NE 
<collectingCountry box="[907,967,1076,1102]" name="India" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">India</collectingCountry>
, 
<taxonomicName box="[978,1182,1076,1103]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Agrisius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="albafuliginosus">
<emphasis box="[978,1182,1076,1103]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">A. albafuliginosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName box="[1235,1429,1076,1103]" class="Insecta" family="Arctiidae" genus="Agrisius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="neofuliginosus">
<emphasis box="[1235,1429,1076,1103]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">A. neofuliginosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Totally five species included in this group (
<bibRefCitation author="Volynkin, A. V. &amp; Dubatolov, V. V. &amp; Kishida, Y." box="[641,878,1112,1139]" pageId="1" pageNumber="568" pagination="128 - 138" refId="ref5469" refString="Volynkin, A. V., Dubatolov, V. V. &amp; Kishida, Y. (2018) On the taxonomy of the genus Agrisius Walker, 1855, with descriptions of two new species from Vietnam and Laos (Lepidoptera, Erebidae, Arctiinae). Zootaxa, 4459 (1), 128 - 138. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4459.1.5" type="journal article" year="2018">
Volynkin 
<emphasis box="[753,803,1112,1138]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="568">et al</emphasis>
. 2018
</bibRefCitation>
). Species of this group can be distinguished from other species-groups by a bilobate bulbous uncus, with lobes terminating by small spines or processes; a valva being oval, membranous, and lacking sclerotized processes; and an aedeagus bearing a small or large prick (
<bibRefCitation author="Dubatolov, V. V. &amp; Kishida, Y." pageId="1" pageNumber="568" pagination="156 - 160" refId="ref5100" refString="Dubatolov, V. V. &amp; Kishida, Y. (2013) Remarks on the species composition of the genus Agrisius, with a description of a new species from Laos (Lepidoptera, Arctiidae: Lithosiinae). Tinea, 22 (3), 156 - 160." type="journal article" year="2013">Dubatolov &amp; Kishida 2013</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
